Whether you are an elite operator or just carry for self defense, many factors can hinder the comfortable and necessary handling of your weapon like blood, sweat, mud, solvent, etc. This service guarantees a firm grip anywhere and every time you handle your weapon. I do custom grip textures on many polymer framed firearms like Glocks, M&P's, XD's, and any other polymer frame that not only looks good but also enhances the grip texture for a practical use.
